# Components And Accessibility

- Use functional components with typed props interfaces.
- Keep component names and helper names clear and typo-free.
- Co-locate component styles (`Component.styles.ts`) when style logic grows.
- For pressable controls, include accessibility role/label/state where relevant.
- Prefer composition and small helpers over monolithic components.
- Remove dead code, temporary UI controls, and unused styles in the same change.
